<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.3.9">
<l>nāṇu niṟaiyuṅ kavarnteṉṉai naṉṉeñcaṅ kūvikkoṇṭu</l>
<l>cēṇuyar vāṉat tirukkun tēva pirāṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>yāṇaiyeṉ ṟōḻī yulaku tōṟalar tūṟṟiyāṅ</l>
<l>kōṇaikaḷ ceytu kutiri yāymaṭa lūrtumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I am sworn, friend,</l>
<l>to the divine lord himself who dwells in far high heaven,</l>
<l>seizing [my] shame and fullnes [and] calling, taking [my] good heart.</l>
<l>We shall mount the palmyra stem as horse , creating troubles</l>
	<l>that will spread gossip in every world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
